OL,3,CMum who had 'barbaric' butt lift op in
OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FA mother-of-three who had "Brazilian
OL,8,Fbutt lift" surgery in Turkey, died
OL,9,Fjust three days after the operation,
OL,10,Ffollowing a catalogue of poor care, an
OL,11,Finquest has heard.
OL,13,FDemi Agoglia, 26, from Salford,
OL,14,FGreater Manchester, died in a hospital
OL,15,Fin Istanbul on 8 January.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@JO]
