OL,3,CMum who had 'barbaric' butt lift op in
OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FShe was said to be "conscious about
OL,8,Fthe way she looked" and was insistent
OL,9,Fon undergoing the BBL procedure, which
OL,10,Fsees fat taken from elsewhere on the
OL,11,Fbody and injected into the hips and
OL,12,Fbuttocks.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, Bolton Coroner John
OL,15,FPollard ruled the medical cause of
OL,16,Fdeath was a microscopic fat embolism
OL,17,Fin which tissue leaks into the
OL,18,Fbloodstream.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@SO]
