OL,3,CMum who had 'barbaric' butt lift op in
OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FHe concluded Ms Agoglia died as a
OL,8,Fresult of misadventure contributed to
OL,9,Fby neglect.
OL,11,FHe said: "I find there was no proper
OL,12,Finformed consent in this matter, there
OL,13,Fwas no proper pre-operative care and
OL,14,Fadvice, and no proper post-operative
OL,15,Fcare.
OL,17,F"All of this meant the care in total
OL,18,Ffell well below the standard expected
OL,19,Fof this type of treatment and the lack
OL,20,Fof care contributed significantly to
OL,21,FDemi's death."
OL,26,@sD@JOUyD@AOU}D@NO]
