OL,3,CMum who had 'barbaric' butt lift op in
OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FHer mother, Christine Tydd, told the
OL,8,Fhearing she told Ms Agoglia she was a
OL,9,F"good looking girl" and did not need
OL,10,Fthe operation, shortly before her
OL,11,Fdaughter travelled to Turkey on
OL,12,FJanuary 4 with her partner, Bradley
OL,13,FJones.
OL,15,FShe said: "She was conscious about the
OL,16,Fway she looked. There was no changing
OL,17,Fher mind."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@SO]wD@KOUyD@JO]
