OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FLandscaper Mr Jones said he also did
OL,8,Fnot want Ms Agoglia to have the
OL,9,Fsurgery, but she had booked the trip
OL,10,Fmonths earlier through a company named
OL,11,FComfort Zone Surgery after "she had
OL,12,Fseen some celebrity" advertising the
OL,13,Fprocedure.
OL,15,FThe couple stayed in a shared villa in
OL,16,FIstanbul before they were taken by
OL,17,Ftaxi to hospital.
OL,19,FFollowing the operation Ms Agoglia was
OL,20,F"shaking" and appeared "very, very
OL,21,Fcold", said Mr Jones.
