OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FStaff from Comfort Zone were called to
OL,8,Fthe villa after Ms Agoglia complained
OL,9,Fof a tight chest and they checked her
OL,10,Fblood pressure but did not inspect the
OL,11,Farea of the operation or check her
OL,12,Fheart rate and pulse, the inquest
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FMs Agoglia collapsed at the villa the
OL,16,Ffollowing day and was taken back to
OL,17,FAvrasya Hospital where she died.
OL,19,FThe surgeon who conducted the
OL,20,Foperation later told Mr Jones they had
OL,21,Fdone everything they could.
