OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FHe said: "The lack of proper care and
OL,8,Fresponse, particularly the failure to
OL,9,Faddress post-operative complications,
OL,10,Fare likely to have played a
OL,11,Fsignificant role in Demi's tragic
OL,12,Foutcome."
OL,14,FDr Tillo said the BBL procedure is
OL,15,Fperformed in the UK "within very
OL,16,Fstrict rules to do it safely".
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@IO]wD@UOUxD@]O]
