OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FPathologist Dr Usha Chandran carried
OL,8,Fout a post-mortem examination on
OL,9,FJanuary 25 and ruled the cause of
OL,10,Fdeath was "unascertained" because she
OL,11,Ffound no evidence of microscopic fat
OL,12,Fembolism.
OL,14,FBut Mr Pollard pointed out that
OL,15,Fdeterioration of the body can take
OL,16,Fplace when there is such a delay
OL,17,Fbetween the death and the post-mortem
OL,18,Fexamination.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@YO]
