OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FDr Tillo agreed with Mr Pollard that
OL,8,Fit would seem "almost incredible" that
OL,9,Fthe death of a young, physically fit
OL,10,Fwoman was not linked to the BBL
OL,11,Foperation she underwent.
OL,13,FDr Chandran told the hearing: "I'm
OL,14,Freally disturbed by Demi's death and I
OL,15,Ffeel all these cosmetic procedures are
OL,16,Fgiven a lot of importance by
OL,17,Fcelebrities... and are being done in
OL,18,Fshoddy clinics."
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@aO]uD@_OUzD@PO]
