OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that the coroner's
OL,8,Foffice had sent multiple emails to the
OL,9,FTurkish hospital and the surgeons
OL,10,Finvolved to obtain statements but had
OL,11,Freceived no response.
OL,13,FMr Pollard said: "Most inquests are
OL,14,Fsad by their very nature. This inquest
OL,15,Fis especially so as it involved the
OL,16,Fdeath of a young woman with
OL,17,Fconsiderable mental health issues who,
OL,18,Fdespite the fact she was pretty and
OL,19,Fher partner did not think she needed
OL,20,Fany improvement, insisted on having a
OL,21,FBBL surgery.
OL,26,@uD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
