OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"I found that she went to Turkey
OL,8,Fpresumably because the process was
OL,9,Fquicker and cheaper than the UK.
OL,11,F"We know little or nothing of the
OL,12,Fperioperative situation because the
OL,13,FTurkish authorities refused to co-
OL,14,Foperate with the coronial process.
OL,16,F"I do find the post-operative care
OL,17,Fvaried from woeful to completely non-
OL,18,Fexistent.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
