OL,3,CMum who had 'barbaric' butt lift op in
OL,4,CTurkey died after poor care, says
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"When she showed obvious symptoms of
OL,8,Fserious illness it was not immediately
OL,9,Frecognised by her partner,
OL,10,Funderstandably, or the unqualified
OL,11,Fmembers of staff.
OL,13,F"By the time she got to the hospital
OL,14,Fit was frankly too late and she was in
OL,15,Fan irrecoverable state.
OL,17,F"I think it was indicative of the poor
OL,18,Flevel of care that at all times she
OL,19,Fwas transported not in an ambulance
OL,20,Fbut in a taxi, it was always the same
OL,21,Ftaxi.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
