OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"I heard extremely helpful evidence
OL,8,Ffrom Dr Tillo who clearly spelt out
OL,9,Fall the failures and failings he was
OL,10,Fable to assess from the evidence and
OL,11,Fthe sparse documentation available to
OL,12,Fhim."
OL,14,FNo record of any intensive care unit
OL,15,Fadmission or of any tests and scans
OL,16,Fcarried out had been produced, the
OL,17,Finquest was told.
