OL,10,FTurkey for any possible surgeries, or
OL,11,Fto research more about it if they are
OL,12,Feven thinking about it.
OL,14,F"She was so beautiful and just didn't
OL,15,Fneed any surgery at all. She only went
OL,16,Ffor the sake of her being so down in
OL,17,Fherself and not feeling good enough.
OL,19,F"Our Dem hasn't just left her family
OL,20,Fbehind, she's left the most beautiful
OL,21,Flittle boys.
